- After writing any code:
  1. Re-read it as a reviewer
  2. Check logic errors
  3. Check missing edge cases
  4. Fix before showing final answer

CODE RULES:
- Keep code simple and readable
- No unnecessary abstractions
- No over-engineering
- Modify only required parts

GOAL:
